law.text:
This subtitle does not:
Diminish any authority of Anne Arundel County, Howard County, or a municipal corporation to license and regulate mobile seafood vendors;
Apply to charitable or nonprofit vendors who sell seafood at short--amp--ndash;term festivals or other short--amp--ndash;term events;
Apply in Calvert County and in St. Mary--amp--rsquo;s County for those persons selling their own seafood catch; or
Diminish the authority of a county to license and regulate mobile produce vendors.
